title: Evicted
description: Being evicted has become a part of Jessa's regular life. Her mom died young, her father a complete train wreck because of it. Jessa starts another new school where she meets the most popular guy and student body president. He's loved and envied by everyone and she finds herself falling hard. She makes herself known to him and the whole school at a vivacious school dance. But what comes with being known? Jealousy, deceit, and hate. With the help of her new friends, she discovers that not everyone's life is perfect. We all have secrets. Will Jessa finally be able to stay still? Or will she lose everything she's worked hard for to another eviction?
author: Traci Sekulovski
